    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA21-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu viṉai muṟṟi mīḷvāṉ tērppākaṟkuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is what the one returning after finishing work said to [his] charioteer.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA21">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            viraippari varuntiya vīṅkucela liḷaiya</l>
<l>            raraicceṟi kaccai yāppaḻit tacaii</l>
<l>            vēṇṭamar naṭaiyar meṉmela varuka</l>
<l>            tīṇṭā vaimuṭ ṭīṇṭi nāñcelaṟ </l>
<l>            kēmati valava tērē utukkā </l>
<l>            ṇurukkuṟu naṟuneyp pālvitirt taṉṉa</l>
<l>            varikkuraṉ miṭaṟṟa vannuṇ palpoṟik</l>
<l>            kāmaru takaiya kāṉa vāraṇam</l>
<l>            peyaṉīr pōkiya viyaṉeṭum puṟaviṟ </l>
<l>            pularā vīrmaṇaṉ malirak keṇṭi </l>
<l>            nāḷirai kavara māṭṭit</l>
<l>            taṉpeṭai nōkkiya peruṅtaku nilaiyē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The fast-going young [warriors], who suffered from the hasty motion,</l>
<l rend="indent">having tied [their] belts tight to [their] bodies [and] rested utterly</l>
<l rend="indent3">exhausted,</l>
<l>may they come slowly, slowly at the pace they wish for.</l>
<l rend="indent">For our going, [the horses] tasting the untasted sharp thorn,</l>
<l>go on with the chariot, charioteer. Look there:</l>
<l>the very befitting state, when the desirable, lovely forest cock,</l>
<l rend="indent2">with many pretty fine spots in its neck [and] a voice cutting</l>
<l rend="indent3">as milk dropped into fragrant ghee which is melted,</l>
<l rend="indent">digs, while it is flooded, the undried moist sand</l>
<l>in the wide long woodland, from which the rain water has gone,</l>
<l rend="indent">hooks, [for her] to seize, the daily prey [and] looks for its female.</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
